Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.48,1:55:21.64,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你想来一个吗  意大利货\NYou want one? They're Italian.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.47,1:55:45.80,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶福特1号的肯·迈尔斯\NKen Miles in Ford number 1
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.80,1:55:47.89,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,和驾驶法拉利21号的班迪尼\Nand Bandini in Ferrari 21
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.89,1:55:49.57,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,在这样恶劣的天气条件下互不相让\Nare locked in a battle against the elements
