Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.20,1:59:04.47,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能换掉竖式总成\Nwhere I can't swap out my upright assembly.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.47,1:59:05.60,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,零件就是零件\NA part is a part.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.60,1:59:07.83,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是刹车钳  刹车盘还是竖式总成\NBe it a brake caliper, a rotor, or an upright assembly,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.83,1:59:10.30,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我想换什么就换什么\Nand I can swap out any damn thing I want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.74,1:59:12.54,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为我们没读过规则手册\NWe read your damn rule book.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.35,1:59:20.57,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,班迪尼进站了  他进站了\NBandini's pitting. He's pitting.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.10,1:59:29.25,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可惜\NOh, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.52,1:59:30.72,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是坏了一条管路\NI think he blew a line.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.72,1:59:32.56,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他刚刚想跟上你的速度\NWell, he was trying to keep up with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.35,1:59:44.75,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不懂意大利语  但是看得出来他不高兴\NI don't speak Italian, but he ain't happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.10,1:59:57.77,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我得赶紧出发了  老爹\NGet me out of here, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.77,1:59:58.92,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-快点  -知道了\N- Come on! - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.92,1:59:59.77,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.77,2:00:02.09,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就好  肯  马上就好\NAlmost there, Ken. Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.69,2:00:03.56,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了  兄弟\NHow's it looking, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.57,2:00:04.78,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,再充点气  就可以了\NOne pump, and we're good.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.40,2:00:06.32,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,可以出发了  肯\NCar's yours, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.32,2:00:07.74,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  你还有赢他的机会\NAll right, listen, you can still take him,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.74,2:00:09.15,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你得超过他两次\Nbut you gotta pass him twice.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.15,2:00:11.24,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  超过他两次\NI get it. Pass him twice.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.04,2:00:20.62,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯·迈尔斯驾驶的福特1号重回赛道\NFord number 1 driven by Ken Miles is back out,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.62,2:00:23.59,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,紧紧咬着班迪尼的法拉利21号\Nhot on the heels of Bandini in Ferrari 21.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.48,2:01:24.77,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够好  迈尔斯  再加把劲\NNot bloody good enough, Miles! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.36,2:01:26.65,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他慢下来了\NHe's off his pace.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.40,2:01:30.61,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在对车还是没有信心\NHe doesn't trust the car yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.82,2:01:33.74,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  肯  刹车我都给你换好了\NCome on, Ken. I gave you new brakes, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.66,2:01:41.00,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.54,2:01:43.83,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里是为了什么\NWhat did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.42,2:01:47.59,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,放手一搏吧\NLet's do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.94,2:02:13.91,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,成了  加油\NThat's it! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.12,2:02:26.58,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他还没做到\NHe ain't done it yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.25,2:02:32.22,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他还需要再追一圈\NHe needs to take another lap on him.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.93,2:02:42.64,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,福特1号  肯·迈尔斯
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.03,2:02:57.74,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要尽快进站\NHe needs to pit soon.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.78,2:02:59.99,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,先追上班迪尼再说\NHe needs to catch Bandini first.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.42,2:03:11.88,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  你这个混蛋\NAll right, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.30,2:03:14.55,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再来一次\NLet's do this again.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.04,2:03:45.46,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,快呀\NCome on, now.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.00,2:03:48.38,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的  好样的\NThat's my girl! That's my girl!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.23,2:04:11.23,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天呐  我的天呐\NOh, my God. Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.52,2:04:12.65,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的\NBloody hell!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:26.75,2:04:28.79,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他做到了  我们领先了\NHe did it. We're in the lead.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.25,2:04:30.46,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我们领先了吗\NAre we in the lead?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.87,2:04:32.29,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,班迪尼呢\NWhat about Bandini?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.25,2:04:34.50,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,班迪尼在哪\NWhere's Bandini?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.13,2:04:37.09,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们完了  结束了\NThey're done. Finished.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.59,2:04:38.80,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,法拉利完了\NFerrari's over.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.80,2:04:40.97,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,迈凯轮的GT落后他四分钟\NMcLaren's four minutes behind him in a GT.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.97,2:04:42.55,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,现在肯排第一\NSo we're lying Ken first,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.55,2:04:44.68,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,第二和第三  也都是福特\Nand two and three. All Fords.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.82,2:05:01.82,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,法拉利21号\NFerrari number 21
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.99,2:05:04.53,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,和车手班迪尼已经离开赛道\Nand driver Bandini have left the track.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.62,2:05:07.91,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,大魔王来了\NThe Deuce is coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.05,2:05:20.09,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯半小时后就要上了  要我叫醒他吗\NKen's up in a half an hour. Want me to wake him?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.09,2:05:21.43,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,不  让他睡吧\NNah, let him sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.14,2:05:25.26,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-非常感谢  -不可思议\N- Thank you very much. - Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.26,2:05:26.26,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,您好  福特先生\NHello. Mr. Ford.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.26,2:05:27.43,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛还没有结束  不过\NWe're not quite there yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.47,2:05:28.31,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你错过了一顿美餐\NYou missed a good meal.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.31,2:05:30.35,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他来了  他来了\NThere he is. There he is.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:32.23,2:05:33.44,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,现在进展如何  里奥\NBrief me, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:34.02,2:05:36.44,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,前三名都是我们的车  福特先生\NWe're running one, two, three, Mr. Ford.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.40,2:05:38.27,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,领头的是谁\NWho's in the lead?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.28,2:05:39.90,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,赫尔姆和迈尔斯\NHulme, Miles.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.36,2:05:44.24,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个想法  福特先生\NYou know, I was thinking, Mr. Ford...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.20,2:05:48.66,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我们的三台车可以排成一排\Nwouldn't it be great if all three Fords lined up
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.66,2:05:51.00,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,同时冲过终点  那该多壮观\Nand crossed the finish line at the exact same time?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.50,2:05:53.50,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们排成一排  一起回家\NThey all lined up and came home together.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.50,2:05:56.13,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,三台福特  并驾齐驱\NFord. Ford. Ford.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.46,2:05:59.09,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不太可能做到  先生\NI don't think we can actually do that, sir, but...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.92,2:06:00.80,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不能\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.88,2:06:03.76,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯现在领先不止一圈  里奥\NMiles is laps ahead, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.76,2:06:06.93,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让他怎么做  减速吗\NWhat would you have him do, slow down?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.64,2:06:09.47,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:17.23,2:06:19.32,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,福特先生想让迈尔斯减减\NMr. Ford wants Miles to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.32,2:06:21.78,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他希望三辆车可以同时冲过终点\NHe wants all three cars to cross at the exact same time.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.78,2:06:23.57,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他认为对福特来说  这将会是历史性的一刻\NHe thinks it'll be a historic moment for Ford.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.57,2:06:25.62,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,拍出来的照片一定赏心悦目\NIt'll make a great photograph.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.99,2:06:29.49,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔比  迈尔斯现在要发挥团队精神\NShelby, Miles needs to be a team player here,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.83,2:06:30.75,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样\Nand so do you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.12,2:06:33.00,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你来告诉他  还是我来说\NYou gonna tell him, or you need me to?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:34.46,2:06:37.21,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,离我的车手远一点  走开\NDon't go near my driver. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.09,2:06:39.46,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,这是福特先生的要求\NThis is what Mr. Ford wants.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.46,2:06:40.55,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,给我走开\NGo on now.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:41.09,2:06:42.80,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-他希望看到你们的忠诚  -走开\N- He expects loyalty. - Go on.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:00.02,2:07:02.23,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,行动起来  小伙子们  动作快点\NGuys, let's go. Come on. All right, look lively, boys.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.23,2:07:03.48,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  弗罗斯特\NLet's go. Frosty.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.49,2:07:04.45,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,来了\NYeah, coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.86,2:07:07.45,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\NLet's go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.45,2:07:08.62,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,毕比要干什么\NWhat's Beebe want?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.12,2:07:16.75,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是很过分的要求\NIt's off the scale, innit?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.05,2:07:23.51,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想让你减速\NThey want you to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.93,2:07:29.60,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你再说一遍\NRun that by me again.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:29.97,2:07:31.43,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想让你减速\NThey want you to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.35,2:07:35.85,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯  你让他们的车相形见绌了\NYou're outshining their car, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:35.85,2:07:37.81,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你领先了迈凯伦四分钟\NYou're four minutes up on McLaren.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.81,2:07:39.27,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,大魔王希望福特的三辆车\NThe Deuce wants the three Fords
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.27,2:07:41.86,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,分别以第一  第二  第三名一起冲过终点线\Nto cross the finish line one, two, three, all together.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.24,2:07:49.57,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要求你有些团队精神\NThey're asking that you be a team player...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.99,2:07:52.70,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助他们拍下那样一张照片\Nand make that photograph happen for 'em.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.70,2:07:56.29,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了拍张照片  他们真行啊\NThat photograph. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.50,2:07:58.42,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,真会想\NThat is good.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.29,2:08:03.25,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯  即便你和他们并列夺冠\NKen, even if you tie for first...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.09,2:08:06.30,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你仍然是史上第一个在同一年内夺下\Nyou'd still be the first man ever to win...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:06.55,2:08:09.30,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,赛百灵  迪通拿  和勒芒三项赛事冠军的人\NSebring, Daytona, and Le Mans in the same year.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.93,2:08:11.43,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你将成为三冠王\NYou'd have the triple crown.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.77,2:08:19.85,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我没有...\NLook, I ain't get...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.56,2:08:23.15,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我从第一天开始\NI haven't been able to get you
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.15,2:08:24.57,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法让你服从命令\Nto follow an order since day one.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.82,2:08:26.82,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你想怎么做我都可以接受\NWhatever you wanna do is fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.61,2:08:29.61,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我做主吗\NMy choice?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.53,2:08:32.53,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你做主\NYour choice.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.58,2:08:40.96,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,发动机已经快到极限了\NThe engine's running at boiling.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:40.96,2:08:42.34,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,刹车也快不行了\NThe brakes are shot.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.05,2:08:47.05,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,安排好了吗\NHow was that?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.97,2:08:50.09,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,都搞定了\NTaken care of.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:50.09,2:08:51.64,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,车准备好了  肯\NThe car's yours, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.76,2:08:53.35,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯  车为你准备好了\NKen, the car's yours.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.64,2:08:55.35,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯\NKen!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.35,2:08:56.64,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,可以出发了  肯\NCar's yours, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:30.30,2:09:32.05,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,所有车手都在追赶福特车队\NIt's the Fords that are the cars to beat,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.05,2:09:33.84,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻他们的三辆车包揽了前三名\Nclaiming the top three positions...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.84,2:09:35.10,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底在做什么\NWhat the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.09,2:09:36.56,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯·迈尔斯驾驶着福特1号位居第一\Nled by Ken Miles in Ford number 1...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.39,2:09:41.60,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,不许接\NDon't answer that.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.73,2:09:42.90,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,离电话远点\NGet away from it.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.19,2:09:44.48,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,离电话远点\NGet away from it.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:44.48,2:09:47.52,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶着福特1号的肯·迈尔斯\NKen Miles in Ford number 1 is demonstrating
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.52,2:09:50.28,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻正以他超凡的车技\Nwhy he's one of the top drivers here at Le Mans
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.28,2:09:52.70,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,展示着为何他是勒芒赛上最出色的车手之一\Nwith an outstanding display of skill.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.82,2:09:54.69,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,观众们请瞧好福特1号\NKeep an eye on Ford number 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.55,2:10:13.17,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他要破他自己的纪录了\NHe's gonna break his own record.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.17,2:10:14.30,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话\NShut up.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.23,2:10:24.27,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\NWait for it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:26.56,2:10:27.52,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,再等等\NWait for it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.98,2:10:31.78,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在\NNow.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.03,2:10:49.67,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯  迈尔斯  迈尔斯\NMiles. Miles. Miles.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:15.86,2:11:16.82,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮\NBellissimo.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.74,2:11:20.99,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,3分30秒6  他又刷新纪录了\N3.30.6. That's another record.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.08,2:11:26.91,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯·迈尔斯时再次刷新了最快圈速\NAnother lap record falls to Ken Miles...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.92,2:11:27.79,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,这是完美的一圈\NIt's a perfect lap.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.79,2:11:29.00,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,打破了他自己的纪录\N...breaking his own record
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.00,2:11:32.75,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,以此为谢尔比美国车队\Nand virtually guaranteeing first place for Shelby American
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.75,2:11:34.55,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,以及他们出色的GT40确保了冠军\Nand their exciting GT40.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.55,2:11:37.51,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶着谢尔比美国车队福特1号的肯·迈尔斯\NKen Miles in Shelby America's Ford number 1
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.51,2:11:39.93,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚打破了他自己创下的圈速纪录\Njust beat his own lap record.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.93,2:11:41.93,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,3分30秒6\NThree minutes and 30.6 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.93,2:11:43.10,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,让他进站\NBring him in.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.18,2:11:45.02,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,马上让他进站  他已经失控了\NRight now! He's outta control.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.10,2:11:47.10,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,在他毁了那辆车  使我们无法完成比赛之前\NNow, you bring him in before he wrecks that car
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.10,2:11:48.48,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,让他进站\Nand we don't finish.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:50.86,2:11:52.02,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,让他进站  谢尔比\NBring him in, Shelby,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.19,2:11:55.24,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我让SCCA和FIA把你的车队禁了\Nor I will get you banned from the SCCA and the FIA.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.20,2:11:55.25,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,SCCA  美国赛车俱乐部\NFIA  国际汽车联盟
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.74,2:11:58.87,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开车的人是肯·迈尔斯  里奥\NKen Miles is behind the wheel, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.07,2:12:00.83,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,如何完成比赛由他决定\NThat's his car to the finish.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:02.37,2:12:04.49,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ 快快乐乐 ♪\N♪ H-a-p-p-y ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:12:04.49,2:12:06.91,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ 我快快乐乐 ♪\N♪ I'm h-a-p-p-y ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:12:06.91,2:12:09.58,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,♪ 我确定一定以及肯定自己很快乐 ♪\N♪ I know I am, I'm sure I am ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:13:36.04,2:13:37.67,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,快呀  伙计们  怎么还没追上来\NCome on, lads, where are ya?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.72,2:13:50.69,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-这真是难得一见的赛况  -他在做什么\N- That is quite a sight to see. - What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.31,2:13:52.68,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  他为什么在减速\NMum, why is he slowing down?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.69,2:13:55.61,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,第二名和第三名的福特赛车紧随其后\N...the second and third place Fords to close ranks.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.26,2:14:27.81,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,三辆福特将会同时冲过终点\NThe three Fords are going to cross the line together.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:27.85,2:14:30.14,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯·迈尔斯减速了  等他的队友追上\NKen Miles slowed down. He waited for them.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:30.14,2:14:32.98,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-现在三辆福特并排前行  -爸爸  不要\N- Here are the Fords lined up in a row... - Dad. No.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.98,2:14:33.89,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-没事的  -爸爸\N- It's all right .- Dad.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.89,2:14:35.48,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-没事的  -一  二  三\N- It's all right. - One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:35.52,2:14:36.27,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他带领着他们\NLook, he's bringing them in.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:36.27,2:14:37.70,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,由肯·迈尔斯引领...\NLed by Ken Miles...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.70,2:14:38.73,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他带领他们一起冲过终点\NHe's bringing them all in together.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:38.73,2:14:40.61,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他毫无疑问是此队的引领者...\N...certainly the leader of this group
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.61,2:14:43.28,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-他刚刚创下勒芒赛...  -干得好\N- and owner of the Le Mans lap record... - Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:43.28,2:14:45.11,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-最快圈速纪录  -肯  干得好\N- ...set just moments ago. - Good for you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.96,2:15:06.18,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  太好了\NYeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.60,2:15:13.68,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这场面\NLook at that.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:16.23,2:15:18.27,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-干得漂亮  里奥  -你也是  唐\N- Well done, Leo. - You too, Don.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:35.41,2:15:36.58,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等\NPlease stand by.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.58,2:15:38.42,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,最终赛果正在审核\NFinal results are under review.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:38.42,2:15:40.29,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,和我解释一下为什么他最先冲过终点\N...is explain to me how he's finished first
Dialogue: 0,2:15:40.29,2:15:41.25,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,却不是第一名\Nand he's not won the race?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:41.25,2:15:43.25,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,因为迈凯伦的起点更靠后\NBecause McLaren started from further,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:43.25,2:15:45.21,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他更...  他赢了\Nso he came in... he won.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.21,2:15:46.59,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,结果不是并列第一\NLook, it's not a tie.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:46.59,2:15:47.38,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,不是并列  因为迈凯伦\NNo, because McLaren...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:47.38,2:15:49.01,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,因为迈凯伦的起点更靠后\NBecause McLaren started further back,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:49.01,2:15:50.80,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他的行驶里程更多一些\Nhe's saying he's traveled that little bit further,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.80,2:15:52.26,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他赢了  而不是肯\Nso he's won and not Ken.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:51.49,2:15:53.26,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,行驶里程更多  他赢了\NIt's a longer distance. He won.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:52.26,2:15:54.35,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,这太扯了  胡扯\NThat is bullshit. That's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:54.35,2:15:56.27,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔  等等\NShel! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.28,2:16:11.33,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,并列第一呢\NWhere's the tie?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:11.91,2:16:13.41,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈不是说并列第一吗\NWhere's the goddamn tie?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.41,2:16:15.70,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -你这个王八蛋\N- What? - You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.70,2:16:16.37,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢尔比  -你早知道会这样\N- Shelby! - You knew!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:16.37,2:16:17.33,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我并不知道\NNo, I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:17.33,2:16:19.50,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-够了  够了  -放开我\N- That's enough! Enough! - Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:20.92,2:16:21.50,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁斯\NBruce.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:21.50,2:16:23.46,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,赛得漂亮  兄弟  祝贺\NNice race, mate. Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:45.40,2:16:46.36,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔\NShel!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:50.91,2:16:52.37,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们抢了你冠军  肯\NThey robbed you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:52.45,2:16:54.24,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,以下是对赛果的澄清\NHere is the clarification.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:54.33,2:16:56.99,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然三名车手同时冲过终点线\NThough the drivers finished the race in a heat,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:56.99,2:16:58.87,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为迈凯伦的起点更靠后\NMcLaren has been ruled the winner
Dialogue: 0,2:16:58.87,2:17:00.66,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他被裁定为冠军\Nas he started from farther back.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:00.67,2:17:01.87,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些胡扯的技术细节\NSome bullshit technicality.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:01.87,2:17:04.42,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,最终结果  由迈凯伦和阿蒙驾驶的\NFinal results. Ford number 2,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:04.42,2:17:07.67,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,福特2号  赢得了比赛的冠军\Ndriven by McLaren and Amon, is the winner.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:07.67,2:17:10.59,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,由迈尔斯和赫尔姆驾驶的福特1号\NFord number 1, driven by Miles and Hulme,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:10.59,2:17:11.80,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,获得了亚军\Nsecond place.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:11.80,2:17:14.43,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,季军是由巴克奴和哈切森\NIn third place, Bucknum and Hutcherson
Dialogue: 0,2:17:14.43,2:17:16.14,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶的福特5号\Nin Ford number 5.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.14,2:17:17.73,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本不该和你说\NI never should've asked you.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.69,2:17:25.48,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了卖车  对吧\NSelling cars, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:28.15,2:17:29.40,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是干这个的\NThat's what they do.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:30.61,2:17:33.99,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你许诺过让我驾驶\NWell, you promised me the drive.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:36.62,2:17:37.58,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,没许诺过夺冠\NNot the win.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.16,2:17:40.41,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你开得太棒了\NIt was a hell of a drive.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.71,2:17:43.17,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们的车很棒\NShe's a hell of a machine.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:44.25,2:17:45.25,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,它确实很快\NShe's fast.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.21,2:17:48.30,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,还能更快\NCould be faster.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:50.51,2:17:52.26,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,7L发动机确实性能绝佳\NThe 7 liter's sweet...
Dialogue: 0,2:17:52.68,2:17:53.68,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,不过\Nbut...
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.89,2:17:56.68,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我们仍然需要轻一些的底盘\Nwe still need a lighter chassis.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:56.68,2:18:00.43,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我在考虑使用复合铝材\NI was thinking bonded aluminium.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:00.43,2:18:03.73,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要从头开始打造  但如果能成\NIt's a ground-up rebuild, but if it works...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.10,2:18:06.35,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,可以减轻几百斤车重\Nwe can lose a couple hundred pounds.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:06.36,2:18:08.07,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们还在这浪费什么时间\NWell, what the hell are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:09.78,2:18:12.11,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,让我回去洗个澡  喝杯茶\NLet me take a shower, get a cup of tea...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:12.45,2:18:14.07,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,再来点火腿奶酪夹面包什么的\Nham and cheese cob or something.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:14.91,2:18:16.83,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明年再来赢这些王八蛋\NWe're gonna get the bastards next year.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.85,2:18:43.39,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,油缸里还剩一点汽油\NGot a bit of fuel left in the tank.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.52,2:18:46.35,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得那些蜂窝板结构的底盘怎么样\NWhat do you think of those honeycomb panels?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:46.35,2:18:48.32,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,是你想要的吗\NWhat you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.44,2:18:49.48,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道\NDon't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:15.34,2:19:16.84,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,这车看起来相当棒\NShe looks pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.40,2:19:30.77,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,在七千转时  有一个临界点\NThere's a point, at 7,000 RPM...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:32.11,2:19:34.28,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都变得虚无\Nwhere everything fades.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:36.86,2:19:39.33,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,车失去了重量\NThe machine becomes weightless.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:40.24,2:19:41.54,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,直接消失了\NJust disappears.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.66,2:19:43.33,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,爽\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:43.33,2:19:45.66,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,只留下一具躯壳\NAnd all that's left is a body...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:45.75,2:19:47.79,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,在时空中穿梭\Nmoving through space and time.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:51.17,2:19:52.88,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,七千转\N7,000 RPM.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:54.21,2:19:55.63,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个临界点\NThat's where you meet it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:57.80,2:19:59.22,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感觉到它的来临\NYou feel it coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:59.43,2:20:01.85,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,它悄悄地逼近你  来到你的耳边\NIt creeps up on you, close in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:10.06,2:20:11.57,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,向你提出一个问题\NAsks you a question.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:12.86,2:20:14.65,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,一个终极的问题\NThe only question that matters.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.41,2:20:21.41,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,把货车开过来\NGet the van!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:23.16,2:20:24.08,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,"你究竟是谁"\N"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.49,2:20:59.32,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉如何\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.32,2:21:02.12,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  感觉好极了\NIt's fantastic. Feels really good.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.66,2:21:03.83,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶感流畅\NNice and smooth.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.78,2:21:07.16,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,变速箱没有振动  感觉马力强劲\NNo vibration in the box. Feels really strong.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.16,2:21:09.12,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你才开了不到一小时\NYou drove it for less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.66,2:21:11.71,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感觉出来个屁\NYou can't tell shit after an hour.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:11.71,2:21:15.30,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,每辆车七千块整  总共就是一万四\NGo for seven even, that'd be 14 all in.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.34,2:21:16.05,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔\NShel.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:18.56,2:21:20.82,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,赛道之星
Dialogue: 0,2:21:26.60,2:21:29.60,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔  那个家伙  就是那个戴帽子的\NShel, that guy, you know the one in the hat,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:29.60,2:21:32.06,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经决定下单两辆眼镜蛇427\Nhe's ready to close on those two 427s.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:32.06,2:21:34.82,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他和他太太一人一辆  全额运费\NHis and hers. Full freight.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.48,2:21:38.11,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是从加尔温斯顿飞过来的\NThey, flew in from Galveston.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.82,2:21:44.74,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你出来个一两分钟\NI need you to come outside for maybe a minute.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:45.41,2:21:46.45,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么\NAnd do what?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:48.41,2:21:49.87,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,做卡罗尔·谢尔比\NBe Carroll Shelby.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.87,2:21:53.75,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,给他们讲个故事  说点吉祥话\NTell them a story, spin a few magic words.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:54.33,2:21:57.17,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,"吉祥话"是什么意思\NWhat does that mean? "Magic words"?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:58.30,2:21:59.42,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是\NIt means...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:59.84,2:22:01.92,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,出来跟他们打个招呼\Ncome outside and say hello
Dialogue: 0,2:22:01.92,2:22:04.05,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们这个钱花得心里舒服\Nand make them feel good about their purchase.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:04.05,2:22:05.34,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们买的是车\NThey're getting the damn cars.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.34,2:22:07.26,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他们花了钱  车就归他们了  菲尔\NThat's what they get for their money, Phil.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.56,2:22:09.01,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,要买就买  不买拉倒\NNow, either they want 'em or they don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:09.02,2:22:10.72,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,-我难道是个戏子吗  -不是\N- Am I some kind of a lounge act? - No.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.73,2:22:12.64,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我难道是个搞推销的吗\NAm I here to talk people into things?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.07,2:22:25.91,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过去六个月了  谢尔\NIt's been six months, Shel.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:27.45,2:22:28.74,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,六个月了\NSix months.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:33.58,2:22:35.63,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候他们不会活着下车\NSometimes they don't get out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:11.12,2:23:12.37,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\NPeter!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:13.33,2:23:15.96,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得  来把垃圾搬出去\NPeter, come and take the garbage out.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:16.08,2:23:17.46,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,谢尔比先生\NMr. Shelby.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:19.34,2:23:20.21,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  彼得\NHello, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:22.51,2:23:24.09,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得那把扳手\NI remember that wrench.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.17,2:23:26.76,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸拿它扔了你\NMy dad threw it at you.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:28.39,2:23:29.56,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\NI believe he did.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.51,2:23:31.35,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:36.69,2:23:38.61,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,好像因为我对他说了些什么\NI think I probably said something to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:39.73,2:23:41.19,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,骂了他几句\NCalled him a few names.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:43.28,2:23:44.44,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.58,2:23:55.21,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你要找我妈妈吗\NDo you wanna speak to my mum?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:55.91,2:23:57.00,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想找她\NWell, I did.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.54,2:24:01.00,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我想来打个招呼  看她过得好不好  还有...\NI came to say hello, check in on her and...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:05.67,2:24:07.63,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我想到  有时候\NThen I started thinking that sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.47,2:24:12.43,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,言语...\Nwords...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.06,2:24:17.10,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有任何用处\Njust... ar-are not useful.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:22.94,2:24:25.28,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,工具是有用的  因为你能用它们造东西\NTools are useful 'cause you can make stuff with 'em
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.28,2:24:27.28,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,也能用它们修东西\Nand you can fix stuff with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:28.53,2:24:29.41,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,给你\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:30.99,2:24:32.03,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:40.88,2:24:42.47,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸是...\NYour daddy was...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:45.96,2:24:47.38,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的朋友\NHe was your friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.76,2:24:54.93,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  他是我的朋友\NYes, he was.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:56.47,2:24:57.82,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  小伙子\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:02.98,2:25:06.03,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,他觉得你是个特别棒的孩子\NAnd he thought you was just finer than frog fur.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:10.53,2:25:11.82,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得\NPeter!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:17.04,2:25:19.04,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去帮妈妈干活了\NI think I've gotta go help my mum.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:21.33,2:25:23.71,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,那你还磨蹭什么呢  快去吧\NWhat are you doing here then? Go on.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.63,2:25:25.59,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:40.38,2:26:45.26,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,肯·迈尔斯深受全世界赛车迷的尊敬\N入选赛车名人堂
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.51,2:26:50.71,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,卡罗尔·谢尔比成为了历史上\N最成功和最有名的赛车设计者之一
Dialogue: 0,2:26:51.14,2:26:56.73,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,由谢尔比和迈尔斯研制的福特GT40\N赢得了1966  1967  1968及1969年的勒芒耐力赛
Dialogue: 0,2:26:57.98,2:27:02.05,外文,NTP,0,0,0,,是迄今为止唯一赢得过\N勒芒24小时耐力赛的美国产赛车

